            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Virtual text won't work if you place in the middle of a multibyte char. Use `virtcol2col()`:\r\n```lua\r\nlocal col = vim.fn.virtcol2col(0, 1, 6) - 1\r\nvim.api.nvim_buf_set_extmark(0, vim.api.nvim_create_namespace(''), 0, col, {virt_text={{\"<--5\", \"TestHl\"}}, virt_text_pos=\"inline\"})\r\n```",
